description:
Joe McNamara (Zoe Saldaña) is the station chief of the CIA's Lioness program. Rewatch memorable moments from Season 2 as she works with Kaitlyn (Nicole Kidman), Byron (Michael Kelly), and Secretary of State Mullins (Morgan Freeman) to enlist a new Lioness operative to infiltrate a previously unknown threat, while confronting the profound personal sacrifices she has made with her husband Neal (Dave Annable) and her children.
